description:
On an all new Unqualified, Whitney Cummings (THE FEMALE BRAIN, WHITNEY) returns to the show to meet Kayla at the Sutton Place Hotel (4:48), play a round of Deal Breakers (10:46), and talk "making sex" with Chad (20:50).

Later, they chat about Whitney's directorial debut: The Female Brain and first date ettiquette (37:00) before taking a call from Alex, who's long distance boyfriend is considering a female roommate (50:05). All that and more on a brand new Unqualified!

 

Go to crowdrise.com/unqualified to donate to GAPPS today. Help increase awareness and fund research towards preventing prematurity and stillbirth in newborn children and you may win a trip to LA to hang out with Anna and the Unqualified crew!
